{"tid":2371483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科興公布相隔三星期接種兩劑疫苗有效率近7成","createTime":"2021-01-19T02:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T02:30:14.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2db989b66a3e55c4729817602d957e74c8796ff5","tid":2371483,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"中國科興生物技術公司公布，在巴西最新臨床測試結果顯示，研發的新型冠狀病毒疫苗，有效率接近7成，較巴西早前公布的數據高接近20個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，1394名參與者相隔三星期接種兩劑疫苗，有效率近70%。而巴西研究人員上星期公布的結果，有效率50.4%，是基於超過9千多名志願者的測試結果，他們大部分相隔兩星期接種兩劑疫苗，但有少部分志願者因為不同原因，較遲才接受第二劑注射。<br />\n<br />\n巴西當局早前對科興和英國阿斯利康藥廠疫苗，批出緊急使用許可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571103-20210119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571103-20210119.htm&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=652ddca3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571103-20210119.htm&h=e866e84a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571103-20210119.htm</a>"},{"pid":"85b82f2e17eb3c0af5cef6904738d3e321c5900d","tid":2371483,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:05:24.000Z","msg":"Biden angle"},{"pid":"7bf42dfe0f39fb867a06505ee1101fc9c5144c7a","tid":2371483,"uid":58630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"上次9千個sample今次得千三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ddad817a071891f5a7e23066f2a25870efd869","tid":2371483,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:10:11.000Z","msg":"用咁耐時間黎諗點set多個條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c66bfc2a0a3e9e9fead1e722e39ed1cef844f70","tid":2371483,"uid":8308,"like